{"type": "article", "id": 24934, "title": "橡胶套环", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-05T07:03:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071042316Lx1H93qsfPXEYC5.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个用来捆扎的橡胶环，按照刻好的纹路向两边拉伸就形成菱形的网格，刚好捆扎一张圆筒状的纸。它也可以套在吃了一半的薯片上，成为密封的办法。如果更用力拉伸就就形成三个连起来的圆环，可以用来分类。这个简单巧妙的小工具也很实用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104228eom42WRDEi7hSGNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.50952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104229gVF8Y04SLmDCHMcf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104229Pnx98VHFoIlXW1Q4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104230Pa5xHAX1p9tUTEKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104230jP2bKM8ldRFIWQmE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}